{"tid":265041,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"當年熱普城屌鳩梁天琦其實都幾仆街","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T16:34:14.000Z","uid":119450,"like":48,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78f2d992016a1f559dec750e42d518a57c61c85c","tid":265041,"uid":119450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"當年梁天琦係魚蛋暴動彈起後就借佢光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱普城選哂五區就講到會讓路俾梁天琦。但事先都唔知有冇同梁天琦商量過<br />\n<br />\n到佢俾人DQ冇哂政治力量個時<br />\n<br />\n暗裡應該開心之外，仲借DQ事件係論壇懶係拎光環<br />\n<br />\n講到要幫佢拎回公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乘機拎票<br />\n<br />\n到本民前到末路，支持青政時<br />\n<br />\n全部熱普城都屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔幫熱普城站台又點？<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋暴動同補選幫過梁天琦少少就成世欠左你？<br />\n<br />\n根本補選冇熱普城幫可能仲多過6萬6票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梁天琦一直沈默已經好厚道<br />\n<br />\n依家睇見熱普城互咬就真係心涼"},{"pid":"a5b09733dfefe29ccf338dd16d9f676d2c1cf855","tid":265041,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"最慘係青政第一個支持本民前參加補選<br />\n又願意比資源本民前用<br />\n但被佢地講到青政痴本民青拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c823e5700bfd88c107ab6efe31fad49d7e3ccf47","tid":265041,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ffd01dddd819a90c6d3849148949d3aa8d83d2","tid":265041,"uid":63801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"熱普城陷家落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95374137dc82104ba000779601535fee5a041472","tid":265041,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"成班人 其實 想玩小圈子遊戲 多過做議員 更唔好講幫香港<br />\n邊撚個退出 邊撚個加入 都可以起一堆爐 屌來屌去 <br />\n<br />\n好像<b