ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁新東補選老實講<br />\n<br />\n冇熱狗支持一定冇六萬六<br />\n<br />\n其他觀點大致同意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔會差好遠囉<br />\n2.28 梁天琦人氣係爆燈<br />\n<br />\n即使係去到7月, 天琦街站要提名選9月立法會,<br />\n提名係排住隊 打蛇餅去簽<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤有試過街站, 市民排隊簽提名咩？ 無呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.resistancelive.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/v1-225x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.resistancelive.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fv1-225x300.jpg&h=b41016a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de6ba08f0230852cec90a814e5b21c395b37f684","tid":265041,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁新東補選老實講<br />\n<br />\n冇熱狗支持一定冇六萬六<br />\n<br />\n其他觀點大致同意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔會差好遠囉<br />\n2.28 梁天琦人氣係爆燈<br />\n<br />\n即使係去到7月, 天琦街站要提名選9月立法會,<br />\n提名係排住隊 打蛇餅去簽<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤有試過街站, 市民排隊簽提名咩？ 無呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.resistancelive.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/v1-225x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.resistancelive.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fv1-225x300.jpg&h=b41016a4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗當時天琦嘅個人魅力好強先有咁多人投票俾佢啫<br />\n9月baggio+蟈屍都冇六萬六<br />\n擺明呢小撮人只係會投天琦掛"},{"pid":"b489de0da3dba446ea4522b07763db343b421a3d","tid":265041,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁新東補選老實講<br />\n<br />\n冇熱狗支持一定冇六萬六<br />\n<br />\n其他觀點大致同意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔會差好遠囉<br />\n2.28 梁天琦人氣係爆燈<br />\n<br />\n即使係去到7月, 天琦街站要提名選9月立法會,<br />\n提名係排住隊 打蛇餅去簽<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤有試過街站, 市民排隊簽提名咩？ 無呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.resistancelive.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/v1-225x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.resistancelive.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fv1-225x300.jpg&h=b41016a4&s={SIZ