83e9517b7","tid":265041,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"暴你老母動"},{"pid":"35c75215a867e3d920a50cf1df2364e6e709dd10","tid":265041,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T19:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暴你老母動</blockquote><br />\n咁激動呀"},{"pid":"fc31075bc41a949f844251c3aa2c9410ea28a59d","tid":265041,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T19:21:53.000Z","msg":"以前係支持佢地，好彩選唔到現哂形<br />\n<br />\n當發場夢"},{"pid":"c2945c2d997e0465893d17e6ce5d991d36e43f2c","tid":265041,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前係支持佢地，好彩選唔到現哂形<br />\n<br />\n當發場夢</blockquote><br />\n結果所謂本土派都係一場戲<br />\n泛民又食哂屎<br />\n大部份年輕人被當成棋子<br />\n最後一點火都被潑熄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dca868287b279589b9f538f77d1c51a3882675e","tid":265041,"uid":67266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰日梁天琦補選輸左 熱普城第二日就出黎宣傳自己九月選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣我到依家都覺得係好肉酸，點兜俾人觀感都唔好<br />\n熱普城成日話補選有幫梁天崎但佢無知恩圖報，<br />\n但佢地幫梁天崎佢地自己都痴到d光環架，<br />\n起碼真係痴到d係勇武既光環，少d俾人話得個講字。<br />\n至於梁天崎，亦係失望，講完。"},{"pid":"20216fb449db2a75210e9019b0fda936658bdcb7","tid":265041,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97551e92c6c476c8d220166c2cdc6e1a701195e4","tid":265041,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"好撚彩上年選舉無投俾青山佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投俾plan b好撚過,<br />\n即使到依刻都無後悔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0310841d091578d2ec01d18e2f63cded1e3a33","tid":265041,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"當年梁天琦係<span style=\"color: red;\">魚蛋暴動</span>彈起後就借佢光環<br />\n<br />\n暴你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n革命呀"},{"pid":"aa0991dc325c364eb15294e81b42a2dce4d65d32","tid":265041,"uid":67266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年梁天琦係<span style=\"color: red;\">魚蛋暴動</span>彈起後就借佢光環<br />\n<br />\n暴你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n革命呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係革命，亦唔係曖動，睇規模最多係騷亂"}]}